473
00:50:53.151 --> 00:50:56.151
You know. I think I'm
actually gonna miss this place.

474
00:50:56.220 --> 00:50:57.819
I know I'm not.

475
00:50:59.173 --> 00:51:02.341
Sugar. it's been a
thin slice of heaven.

476
00:51:02.409 --> 00:51:04.104
