choosing another road</i>

518
00:56:27.518 --> 00:56:30.418
down here with the rest of us.

519
00:56:31.671 --> 00:56:33.137
Maybe.

520
00:56:46.336 --> 00:56:51.340
<i>The past has kept you
locked up long enough.</i>

521
00:56:51.408 --> 00:56:56.911
<i>Today. there's really only one
question left to ask yourself.</i>

522
00:56:59.450 --> 00:57:03.418
<i>What are you going to do now?</i>

